    <item>
      <title>拉加德称美国大选获胜者应警惕损害贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/lagarde-says-us-election-winner-should-beware-of-hurting-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，无论谁赢得美国大选，都应警惕损害全球贸易，并再次捍卫自由贸易的好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/lagarde-says-us-election-winner-should-beware-of-hurting-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 16:06:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京会晤使英国太平洋峰会黯然失色，各国领导人选择退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/putin-meeting-overshadows-uk-pacific-summit-as-leaders-opt-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 驳斥了人们对其首次英联邦峰会被弗拉基米尔·普京的金砖国家峰会所掩盖的担忧，此前一些领导人选择不参加英联邦峰会，转而会见俄罗斯总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/putin-meeting-overshadows-uk-pacific-summit-as-leaders-opt-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗拉加称巴西必须在全球舞台上捍卫西方理想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/brazil-must-stand-for-western-ideals-on-global-stage-fraga-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西前央行行长、Gavea Investimentos 创始人阿米尼奥·弗拉加 (Arminio Fraga) 表示，在分裂的全球舞台上，巴西必须明确与西方的民主和人权理想保持一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/brazil-must-stand-for-western-ideals-on-global-stage-fraga-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 15:47:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大学新生入学率出现 2020 年以来首次下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/freshman-enrollment-at-us-colleges-shows-first-drop-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国国家学生信息中心的初步数据，美国大学报告 2024 年秋季新生入学人数下降了 5%，这是自新冠疫情爆发（当时下降了 10%）以来的首次下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/freshman-enrollment-at-us-colleges-shows-first-drop-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 15:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nubank 首席执行官表示，Milei 领导下，Nubank 将重新审视阿根廷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/nubank-taking-new-look-at-argentina-under-milei-ceo-velez-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nu Holdings Ltd. 首席执行官戴维·贝莱斯 (David Vélez) 表示，由于整个拉丁美洲都支持总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 的成功，该公司正在重新评估阿根廷的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/nubank-taking-new-look-at-argentina-under-milei-ceo-velez-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:20:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯经济火爆已过 未来前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/russia-s-red-hot-war-economy-passed-its-peak-with-future-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析人士表示，尽管俄罗斯军工生产强劲，以支持乌克兰持续的战争，但俄罗斯战时经济增长在上半年过热之后，已过了高峰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/russia-s-red-hot-war-economy-passed-its-peak-with-future-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 12:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利总统奥尔班支持率下降 面临反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/hungary-s-orban-tears-into-opposition-as-his-support-dwindles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班周三与反对党发生了紧张冲突，因为一项民意调查显示，其对手彼得·马扎尔 (Peter Magyar) 的新兴政党首次取得领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/hungary-s-orban-tears-into-opposition-as-his-support-dwindles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 11:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京称金砖国家峰会表明“多极世界”正在兴起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/putin-says-brics-summit-shows-a-multipolar-world-is-emerging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京表示，金砖国家扩大后，标志着一个“多极世界”的形成，对美国主导的全球秩序形成挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/putin-says-brics-summit-shows-a-multipolar-world-is-emerging</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 10:22:03 GMT</pubDate>
